Thank you so much
for your time.

950
00:47:34,917 --> 00:47:36,792
Ah, Mr. Roberts.
We can now slip into something

951
00:47:36,875 --> 00:47:38,917
-a little bit more comfortable.
-(SIGHS)

952
00:47:38,999 --> 00:47:40,667
