I don't trust him. Okay?

995
00:49:51,500 --> 00:49:52,999
Your firm has been very tough.

996
00:49:53,083 --> 00:49:54,375
Yeah, too fucking right.

997
00:49:55,583 --> 00:49:57,458
-Harassment?
-Yeah.

998
00:49:57,541 --> 00:50:00,708
Visits at night,
