Weird email stuff. I mean, I--
I... don't want to accuse you--

1000
00:50:05,708 --> 00:50:08,625
No, it's perfectly possible.

1001
00:50:08,708 --> 00:50:10,416
Yeah, I mean,
it's out-sourced security,

1002
