You've broken ranks,
you're in a new category.

1012
00:50:32,416 --> 00:50:33,792
Uh-huh.

1013
00:50:33,875 --> 00:50:36,750
But, look... I wanna clean up.

1014
00:50:37,458 --> 00:50:38,625
I need it all out there.

1015
