1016
00:50:40,708 --> 00:50:44,458
I wanna fire these bastards.
And I want you to help me.

1017
00:50:45,333 --> 00:50:47,375
Sure.

1018
00:50:47,458 --> 00:50:51,917
Well, I guess, you know,
the only question
I would have for you is just...

1019
