it was a stowaway.

1028
00:51:21,958 --> 00:51:23,625
"No real person involved."

1029
00:51:24,625 --> 00:51:25,625
Right.

1030
00:51:28,999 --> 00:51:30,667
Hey, you want to sit down?

1031
00:51:32,833 --> 00:51:34,249
I mean, the good thing is,

1032
