1110
00:55:44,249 --> 00:55:45,458
Thank you.

1111
00:55:50,875 --> 00:55:53,291
LOGAN: So, are you okay, kiddo?

1112
00:55:53,375 --> 00:55:55,958
Yeah. Yeah, good.

1113
00:55:56,041 --> 00:56:00,875
You, uh... You feeling--
