I'm, uh...
I'm sorry if it was rough.

1115
00:56:04,333 --> 00:56:09,833
No, it was... it was fine.
We're good. It's all good.

1116
00:56:09,917 --> 00:56:13,583
Hey, Logan? Rhea's here,
