1117
00:56:13,667 --> 00:56:15,625
Okay.

1118
00:56:15,708 --> 00:56:17,792
-You remember Naomi Pierce?
-LOGAN: Yeah, yeah.
-KENDALL: She came down to--

1119
00:56:17,875 --> 00:56:19,083
-Hi.
-KENDALL: ...to support us.

1120
00:56:21,333 --> 00:56:24,625
