1128
00:56:48,583 --> 00:56:52,458
Well, it's all... You know.

1129
00:56:53,958 --> 00:56:56,375
It goes a long way back.

1130
00:56:56,458 --> 00:56:58,875
Did you-- Did you ever
have an editor

1131
